'''''Martelella''''' is a genus of [[Gram-negative]], [[oxidase]]- and [[catalase]]-positive, strictly [[Aerobic organism|aerobic]], non-[[spore]]-forming [[bacteria]] from the family of [[Aurantimonadaceae]].<ref>[https://www.uniprot.org/taxonomy/293088 UniProt]</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1099/ijs.0.63438-0| title = ''Martelella mediterranea'' gen. nov., sp. nov., a novel  -proteobacterium isolated from a subterranean saline lake| journal = International Journal of Systematic and Evolutionary Microbiology| volume = 55| issue = 2| pages = 955| year = 2005| last1 = Rivas | first1 = R.| pmid=15774691}}</ref>

